{"id":29859,"date":"2024-01-15T19:09:08","date_gmt":"2022-01-15T13:39:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=29859"},"modified":"2022-08-30T15:34:35","modified_gmt":"2022-08-30T10:04:35","slug":"bedroom-design-trends-2022","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/bedroom-design-trends-2022\/","title":{"rendered":"What Are The Bedroom Trends For 2022?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>These bedroom design trends of 2022 will make your home interiors the talk of the town<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The bedroom is the most relaxing space in your home. It is the space that encompasses you into a cosy vibe and takes you away from the external world\u2019s humdrum. The past two years have taken a toll on our mental and physical health. It has taught us the value of our homes and the peace and tranquility that a cosy and functional home adds to our life. With the advent of a New Year, our homes deserve a makeover. So we thought of bringing you the latest in 2022 bedroom trends and giving you a glimpse of what will be in this year. These bedroom design trends are easy to incorporate and will blend seamlessly into your modern design aesthetics. So get ready to explore the bedroom trends of 2022.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bedroom Color Trends For 2022 That Will Catch Your Eye<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When talking of trends, we cannot ignore the latest Pantone colour trend named, Very Peri. This colour instantly livens up your space and lends a joyous vibe. If you are opting for a darker shade like the one shown in the image, be mindful of adding ample lights to illuminate your space. Use an upholstered extended headboard to add to the luxury of the space. We have added a modular wardrobe with a tinted glass front to cut the monotony of bold colour walls and look lighter to the eye. Place a mirror on the accent wall and some lamps on either side of the bed to complete the look of your trendy bedroom design.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye.jpg\" alt=\"Trending bedroom design color trends or 2022 that will catch your eye \" data-id=\"29860\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29860\" class=\"wp-image-29860\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15180524\/trending-bedroom-design-color-trends-or-2022-that-will-catch-your-eye-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Ace the bedroom color trends with Very Peri <\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trending Bedroom Furniture And Accents To Jazz Up The Industrial Design Sensibilities<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Industrial-style bedrooms have been the talk of the town for the last few seasons and are sure to be in trend this year as well. The rugged and edgy vibe it brings to your urban bedroom is beyond comparison. To ace this style, you can opt for a brick cladding wall, cushioned upholstered bed and an accent bucket chair. Add some indoor plants to infuse some freshness into your bedroom and throw in some bulb chains to set a warm tone. We have used wooden flooring and a floor rug to match the colour tone. To add to the frame, you can choose a wooden canopy bed. This will infuse a contemporary look to your uber-cool industrial-style bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities.jpg\" alt=\"Trending bedroom design furniture and accents to jazz up the industrial design sensibilities\" data-id=\"29861\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29861\" class=\"wp-image-29861\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181121\/trending-bedroom-design-furniture-and-accents-to-jazz-up-the-industrial-design-sensibilities-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Industrial-style bedrooms are trending in 2022<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Functional And Space-Saving Bedroom Design Trends For Compact Apartments<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Smart space-saving furniture is trending this year too. They are very efficient in adding additional storage without eating up your floor space. One of the most popular bedroom furniture trends in 2022 is the Murphy bed. These are easy to use and extremely compact. You can pull it down before sleeping and put it back when not in use. Some Murphy beds come with a folding sofa unit that elevates your space&#8217;s functionality by several notches. We have also added some wardrobes with mirror front to create an illusion of a bigger space while helping you with a clutter-free arrangement. This room can be used as a bedroom and a hobby room, making it perfect for compact apartments.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments.jpg\" alt=\"Functional and space-saving 2022 bedroom trends for compact apartments\" data-id=\"29862\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29862\" class=\"wp-image-29862\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181323\/functional-and-space-saving-2022-bedroom-trends-for-compact-apartments-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Enjoy better functionality with modular furniture<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Want to know what kind of bedroom designs suits you\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/02170353\/what-kind-of-bedroom-designs-suits-you.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cosy Minimalistic Spaces Are The Hottest Bedroom Design Trends in 2022&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Minimalistic design trends are quite in this season. Be it the bohemian design, wabi-sabi designs or the ikebana home interiors. You can incorporate these design aesthetics in your bedroom too. Opt for simple and minimalistic designs and accents like raw wood furniture, rattan accent chairs and a wooden beamed ceiling. Pair it up with some indoor plants for a touch of green in your home decor, and you&#8217;re good to go. We used some rattan pendant lights and a macrame wall hanging to beautify the room with a matching theme. Choose a jute or cotton floor rug to stitch the look together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022.jpg\" alt=\"Cosy minimalistic spaces are the hottest trending bedroom design in 2022\" data-id=\"29863\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29863\" class=\"wp-image-29863\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15181851\/cosy-minimalistic-spaces-are-the-hottest-trending-bedroom-design-in-2022-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Simple furniture is a bedroom design trend in 2022<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Traditional Looks Are Trending In Master Bedroom Ideas This Year<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Traditional home interiors lend an elegant look to your space and make your room look grand. The jali woodwork on the false ceiling and abundance of wood in the decor brings in a unique luxury touch. Add a Madhubani painting on the wall to accentuate the look. You can use some spotlights on the false ceiling to bring attention to the intricate carvings on the ceiling. Add a small study desk and an ergonomic chair to create a cosy study space, where you can take your work calls and get done with your office work. Place a decorous floor carpet to stitch the look together and ace one of the most beautiful bedroom design trends of 2022.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-5 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year.jpg\" alt=\"Traditional 2022 bedroom trends where looks are trending in master bedroom ideas this year\" data-id=\"29864\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29864\" class=\"wp-image-29864\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182103\/traditional-2022-bedroom-trends-where-looks-are-trending-in-master-bedroom-ideas-this-year-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Introduce a touch of traditional in your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Bench With Storage Helps Create A Clutter Free Arrangement In Your Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you are looking for some purposeful bedroom furniture trends in 2022, a bed bench is a very functional piece. It helps add additional seating options and storage space for a clutter-free arrangement. You can use it to store your bedsheets, pillows and other bedroom essentials. You could also place the bench beside the window. This way you can have evening coffee with your partner while enjoying the outside view. Cushioned seating, pillows and throws on the bench are enough to create a cosy corner in your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room.jpg\" alt=\"Trending bedroom design bench with storage helps create a clutter free arrangement in your room\" data-id=\"29865\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29865\" class=\"wp-image-29865\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15182342\/trending-bedroom-design-bench-with-storage-helps-create-a-clutter-free-arrangement-in-your-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Introduce a touch of traditional in your bedroom<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Trending Wallpaper For Bedroom To Nurture The Nature Lover In You<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Wallpaper elevates the look of your home instantly and is relatively easy to install. This year there are quite a few trending wallpapers for the bedroom that are getting popular, but the most sought after is the biophilic wallpaper or natural murals. These are the easiest way to add an element of nature to your home interiors without worrying about maintenance. You can add some potted plants to add to the biophilic interior design theme. Opt for an extended headboard in red to create a striking contrast against the green background. Pendant lights, a decorous chandelier and wooden flooring are enough to jazz up your super trendy <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/bedroom-design\/\">bedroom design<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-7 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you.jpg\" alt=\"Trending wallpaper for 2022 bedroom trends to nurture the nature lover in you\" data-id=\"29868\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=29868\" class=\"wp-image-29868\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/01\/15190253\/trending-wallpaper-for-2022-bedroom-trends-to-nurture-the-nature-lover-in-you-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">Biophilic design aesthetics are trending this year<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoyed the list of bedroom design trends for 2022. If you want some expert designers to help you with the home interiors and make your home functional and beautiful, book a free consultation today. Our personalised designs, quick turnaround time and high-quality materials are sure to turn your house into your dream haven. Take care of your near and dear ones and stay healthy. Here\u2019s wishing you a healthy and prosperous 2022!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Lets plan your home interiors together, speak to designers now\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/28124401\/lets-plan-home-interiors-together.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you enjoyed reading about 2022 bedroom trends, also explore about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/home-decor-trends\/\">home decor trends<\/a>.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Pers